  "title": "SHIPPING EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>• Handle all aspects of shipment (land, air-freight and sea-freight)</p><p>• Assisting in shipping and coordination work that includes frequent communication with courier, forwarders and oversea agent</p><p>• Handling and preparation of import and export documentations</p><p>• Handling of LC, permit declaration (OO, II, RM, DP)</p><p>• Preparation of certificates of origin</p><p>• Ensure all billings are done timely and accurately with all necessary supporting documents</p><p>• Tracking of shipments</p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>• Minimum 2 years of relevant working experience in handling shipping by air / sea internationally</p><p>• Knowledge of international trades and shipping</p><p>• Knowledge of import and export documentation</p><p>• Team player, self-motivated and independent. Strong interpersonal skills</p><p>• Transport provided</p><p></p>",
